    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers an accessible entry point for someone looking for straightforward transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but presents a practical value for the right buyer who wants room in the budget for personal updates or repairs. Offered with transparent positioning and real potential at an attractive price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that could make a great budget commuter, first car, or project. It\u2019s priced to reflect its condition and gives someone a chance to get on the road without spending a fortune. If you want simple, straightforward, and affordable, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with a strong-running powertrain, honest wear, and good bones. The engine pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels usable for someone who wants an affordable driver they can sort over time. Expect cosmetic blemishes and age-related needs, but it\u2019s a straightforward platform with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Priced to move and ideal for a mechanically minded owner looking for value.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest cheap car. Rough around the edges, but solid value for the money. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, hard-earned character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a well-traveled machine with real presence and plenty of story left to write. Perfect for a hands-on buyer, first project, or anyone looking for affordable wheels with personality, it offers a chance to step into ownership without a big upfront spend. There\u2019s charm here for the right person: a solid starting point, a distinctive look, and the satisfaction of bringing something seasoned back into the spotlight. If you appreciate potential over polish, this one is easy to imagine as your next practical runabout or weekend revival.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a straightforward opportunity for the right buyer. Ideal as an affordable project, parts vehicle, or basic transportation, it offers solid value for someone who appreciates a practical purchase at an accessible price point. A smart chance to own a vehicle without overspending.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of character? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transport or a fun little project. A good fit for a handy buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it some TLC, and priced fairly to reflect that. If you want something approachable, affordable, and full of potential, come take a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Well-used but still appealing, this car offers solid mechanical character and a straightforward platform for someone who wants an affordable driver or project. The powertrain feels eager, the chassis remains composed, and it has the kind of honest, analog road feel enthusiasts appreciate. Cosmetically it shows its age and needs attention, but underneath it\u2019s a serviceable vehicle with plenty of potential for cleanup, continued daily use, or a weekend build. If you want something inexpensive with usable bones and real upside, this is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
